to move a piece, it is inert, it has no idea

00:18:25.250 --> 00:18:30.840
what role it is playing in the game, and then,
after it has moved, it becomes inert again,

00:18:30.840 --> 00:18:35.130
and waits for the next moment where the chess
player will probably touch it.

00:18:35.130 --> 00:18:36.919
That’s the life of the chess game.

00:18:36.919 --> 00:18:39.900
That’s what we think parenting is.

00:18:39.900 --> 00:18:40.900
Sorry!

00:18:40.900 --> 00:18:41.900
No!

00:18:41.900 --> 00:18:43.850
